		<div class="post-content">
  				<ul id="tpcrn-breadcrumbs"><li><a href="http://www.crystaldiary.com">Home &raquo;</a> </li><li><a class="vca" href="http://www.crystaldiary.com/category/articles/">Articles &raquo;</a></li><li class="current">HE CAME IN A TELEGRAM</li></ul>						
